{"tid":2006650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"優品360料全年盈利大跌8成","createTime":"2020-05-08T02:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-08T02:50:40.000Z","uid":184679,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2826fea4a389f49fa714eb619017b8a818f1bfa8","tid":2006650,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:38:41.000Z","msg":"優品360 （02360） 發盈警，截至2020年3月底止，預計全年純利按年大減80%。優品360解釋，主要原因是香港發生的社會運動，以及新型冠狀病毒的爆發，均對集團零售店舖的正常業務營運造成負面影響。<br />\n<br />\n優品360於2018/19財年盈利5972.8萬元，以盈警公告按年倒退8成，優品360全年盈利約1200萬元。公司截至去年9月底止半年純利下跌6%至1346萬元，反映優品360下半財年業績急惡化，但仍能保持盈利。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2637243/%E3%80%90%E9%9B%B6%E5%94%AE%E5%AF%92%E5%86%AC%E3%80%91%E5%84%AA%E5%93%81360%E7%9B%88%E8%AD%A6%E6%96%99%E5%85%A8%E5%B9%B4%E5%B0%91%E8%B3%BA8%E6%88%90%E3%80%80%E6%97%A9%E5%B8%82%E6%9C%AA%E6%9C%89%E5%8D%87%E8%B7%8C?mtc=20038</code></pre>"},{"pid":"0b57beb52ee8086ca0c90e4266b28afd512861a2","tid":2006650,"uid":87688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:39:45.000Z","msg":"仲有錢賺"},{"pid":"791f9ac882fd75f8b86022ed9aabc229c92205d8","tid":2006650,"uid":161935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"咁都仲有2成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來有2成顧客係中意被福建佬用刀斬到殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"15bb656ad55e533fdd6fcb8735e6f2a810638b9a","tid":2006650,"uid":240890,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"791f9ac882fd75f8b86022ed9aabc229c92205d8","tid":2006650,"uid":161935,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:41:04.000Z","msg":"咁都仲有2成<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原來有2成顧客係中意被福建佬用刀斬到殘廢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-08T02:42:06.000Z","msg":"一定有<br />\n經過成日見到有人買野<br />\n大把c9會去掃貨"},{"pid":"913512fafae06dc2561e30875a1f1ee56697